Romania’s BRD Sees 2011 Net Income Stable or Rising ‘Slightly’

-- B y   I r i n a   S a v u
-- 
2011-03-14T07:03:23Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-03-14/romania-s-brd-sees-2011-net-income-stable-or-rising-slightly-.html
  BRD-Groupe Societe Generale (BRD)  SA,  Romania ’s second-largest bank by assets, said its consolidated
net income will probably be stable or “slightly” increase in
2011, after posting a drop last year, as bad-loan costs will
remain stable or “slightly decrease,” according to a statement
on its website.  To contact the reporter on this story:
